{"tid":1088610,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"現金大抽獎計劃","createTime":"2019-04-02T07:31:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-02T08:23:34.000Z","uid":213411,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f1a55a01b6054e7093ae4c5a734df1517320ce09","tid":1088610,"uid":213411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T07:31:14.000Z","msg":"成日見人網上講 細老我想試下真係同大家玩一次<br />\n每位參加者擺低10蚊 之後抽一個人一注獨得<br />\n我諗一人10蚊呢到都集到一萬銀掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為免各位講乜攪手呃錢<br />\n集錢同抽獎我會採用最多人提議方法<br />\n<br />\n利益申報定細老我淨係負責攪<br />\n我一蚊手續費都唔會抽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n彩池入面一定唔會有我同我家人<br />\n<br />\n10/4/2019前落實到方案我就會落手攪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"001bfbc7c4a270c4d85ee8ebb6662b3df600854f","tid":1088610,"uid":92278,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T07:32:55.000Z","msg":"花式搏拉?"},{"pid":"3daacf537021cbd7c803d44e539fad49c58d994b","tid":1088610,"uid":9328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T07:33:36.000Z","msg":"洗定八月十五"},{"pid":"bbd7ca6e3592d2c652e654e302cc050f9b40724b","tid":1088610,"uid":84159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T07:35:06.000Z","msg":"之前係網上做過類似既野 好快就入左去兩碌<br />\n岩岩出返黎 第時入去之前有咩需要可以問我 記得煙仔好重要 用猛龍食可以一飛分幾次食"},{"pid":"65f68bcdb7a02c12f1a22c9b46d21f68e372558f","tid":1088610,"uid":194012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T07:35:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3b2118ba2b443a9903bb075a569c88a88322afd","tid":1088610,"uid":213411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T07:37:58.000Z","msg":"咁都要比人拉 政府癲鳩左呀"},{"pid":"ada3b457575f6b606982